{"tid":419283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航班改時間零通知　苦主：坐快運壓力大到爆","createTime":"2017-09-30T11:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T11:20:58.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d85dfecf69e9459746b65d5bd03e2118a4b115","tid":419283,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170930/photo/bkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170930142426\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170930142426&h=5ee557d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天(30日)仍有旅客乘香港快運航班出發。(何駿軒攝)<br />\n<br />\n香港快運(HK Express)突然取消下月初多班航機，有旅客紛紛在網上群組留言，指被快運「悄悄地」更改航班，令早前已訂票的旅客頓成驚弓之鳥，擔心成為下一個「受害者」。<br />\n<br />\n有旅客在Facebook群組「HK Express苦主關注組」留言指，原本11月2日上午7時由香港前往日本名古屋，自行以應用程式查閱最新航班情況時，才發現已被改至同日下午6時出發，至今仍未收到快運電郵通知。他坦言由於行程首天已訂了車前往另一個地方，已選擇退錢，改購其他航空公司機票「坐佢(HK Express)壓力大到爆」。<br />\n<br />\n其他旅客亦擔心已訂購的機票受影響，直言「唉，死啦，攪單咁嘅嘢，已經買咗6/11飛東京機票，車同酒店都book晒，都唔知好冇買過其他航空公司D(啲)機票好？」有網民回應指，11月中前往台中，已改買另一班航空公司機票。<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170930/photo/bkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170930142426\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170930142426&h=06fbfef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有旅客在快運無主動通知下更改航班。(「HK Express苦主關注組」fb)<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170930/bkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170930%2Fbkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001.html&d=P9li7PRKRRlwFvomZPFEw54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ffa54a7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170930/bkn-20170930134128210-0930_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a743cdc8ec9eea2a5245c01379325518a40b9838","tid":419283,"uid":83411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"真係唔明點解有人坐呢間咁既垃圾"},{"pid":"1d370ed1b008390d38268ce309c4ddbc45d59f21","tid":419283,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"貪平呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b784e8d7deddcbaebb084b89497c3bf29d0c2a","tid":419283,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"當時搶購到係咪好開心呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141a89bbdc72390ed285fb5ac9ba98d0ade0ac3f","tid":419283,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:06:32.000Z","msg":"我搭過幾次都冇問題，其實比得咩錢嘅就預咗咩服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4481a9d78af014564703167832ab4080b211955","tid":419283,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"去旅行去到咁為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9942828a45104e40199b9ac1dd7c0ce4a281695f","tid":419283,"uid":4761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我搭過幾次都冇問題，其實比得咩錢嘅就預咗咩服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾得咩錢預左無機飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16a01bd72b7e9c4cf70c51c4781eb659de4d410","tid":419283,"uid":4761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行去到咁為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票有咁平得咁平，用黎食好啲住好啲，咁先係去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ee48ef962ee06e02713b252ac480c99e0b085e","tid":419283,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"貪平的垃圾乘客<br />\n下次特價咪又係餓狗搶屎